// https://openprocessing.org/sketch/1188858
// Physarum Letters by jasontothenextone
// A physarum simulation with type
// Sliders control smell distance, a rotating cube, and the letter
// Attribute
// “Physarum Letters” by jasontothenextone
// http://openprocessing.org/sketch/1188858
